.Game
Gosub Init
Use Slice 1
Use BitMap 2
Cls 0
RGB 0,0,2,1
Use Slice 0
RGB 0,0,1,0
Use BitMap 0
Cls 0
Use BitMap 1
Cls 0
Show 1,32,32

If (level MOD 7)=0
  lifes+1
  Mex {-1,135,"    BONUS LIFE"}
  VWait 60
  Cls 0
EndIf

