  Use BitMap 2
  Boxf 100,0,351,19,0
  ll.b=QLimit(lifes,0,8)
  For n=1 To ll
    Blit 127,300-20*ll+20*n,2
  Next
  Use Slice 0
  Use BitMap db
  Return

